Quick Install Instructions:

 tar xjf noc-kit-@PACKAGE_VERSION@.tar.bz2 && \
  cd noc-kit-@PACKAGE_VERSION@ && \
  mkdir build && \
  cd build && \
  ../configure && \
  make && \
  make install

(or use "tar xJf noc-kit-@PACKAGE_VERSION@.tar.xz" above to extract an xz archive).

See INSTALL file for more details.

